## Repository safety rules
- No remote push without an explicit request.
- Commit only the files for the current story; never `git add -A` over unrelated work.
- Never overwrite an existing file without showing a diff and asking.

## Required gates
- Deterministic gates that must pass: <test / lint / build, or N/A>.
